      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm starting work on a new streetwear line and i really want to make sure i'm doing it right. i don't want it to feel like cultural appropriation or anything, you know? can you help me understand what the \"authentic\" aesthetic of urban culture is actually like? like, what are the core visual elements i should look for so it feels real and not like a caricature?",
