      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense, definitely don't want to be that person. But I need some more concrete stuff for my mood boards. If I'm looking at specific vibes, what kind of looks or specific items are we talking about when people say \"urban\"? Like, if I'm trying to capture that essence, what are the specific clothes, colors, or \"street\" details that define it?",
